    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been really well-loved? This beauty is in great shape and ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s been super dependable for me, and I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the maintenance so it drives like a dream. It\u2019s got a few miles on it, but it\u2019s solid and honestly looks fantastic. Perfect if you want something high-quality without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're gonna love it!",
