    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.1) is a driver-focused example featuring the 3.8L M97 flat-six powerplant, delivering 355 hp with a linear power band. Mated to a precise G97 6-speed manual transaxle, the drivetrain exhibits excellent synchro engagement and a firm clutch bite. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing adaptive damping that remains taut through high-G cornering. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system overhaul and a borescope inspection to confirm cylinder wall integrity. While the Arctic Silver finish shows minor road-rash consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this an ideal candidate for a purist seeking a communicative, naturally aspirated 911.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Runs well. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Maintenance up to date.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior showcases a vibrant finish that has been regularly waxed, though you will find the occasional light stone chip consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the upholstery remains supple with no significant wear on the bolsters, and all electronic features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts smoothly, a testament to its consistent service history. We have recently performed a full fluid flush and tire rotation, ensuring it is ready for the road immediately. The undercarriage is clean, and the seals remain tight, providing a quiet, composed ride that feels sturdy and dependable. This is a car that has been respected by its owner and is ready to provide many more years of service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a commitment to both mechanical integrity and aesthetic preservation. Balancing spirited performance with sophisticated styling, this specimen offers a refined driving experience tailored for the discerning professional. It represents a premier opportunity for those seeking a high-caliber vehicle that delivers consistent reliability and distinguished presence.",
