    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and it\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for its next adventure without any worries. It drives super smoothly and has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take a look!",
