    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a 2014 Porsche Cayman (981), a superlative example of mid-engine engineering. This chassis is powered by a 2.7L naturally aspirated horizontally opposed six-cylinder engine, offering a linear torque curve and a high-revving character. The powertrain is paired with a short-throw 6-speed manual gearbox, ensuring maximum driver engagement and tactile feedback. The vehicle features a low center of gravity and optimized MacPherson strut suspension, providing exceptional turn-in response and lateral stability. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive inspection of the cooling system and a fresh set of high-performance tires. While the exterior shows minor road-rash typical of a driven enthusiast car, the mechanical components\u2014including the cross-drilled rotors and four-piston monobloc calipers\u2014are in excellent operating order. This is a purist\u2019s specification, prioritizing mechanical synergy and weight distribution over driver aids.",
